 (wrestler)|Big E]] and [[Kofi Kingston]])\n|align=center | 6<br><small>(5, 6, 5)</br> \n|align=center | April 17, 2020\n|align=center | {{age in days|month1=4|day1=17|year1=2020}}\n|align=center | [[Orlando, Florida]]\n|[[Big E (wrestler)|Big E]] defeated previous champion [[The Miz]] and [[Jey Uso]] in a [[triple threat match]] on ''[[WWE Smackdown|Smackdown]].''\n|}\n\n=== NXT ===\n{|class=\"wikitable\" style=\"font-size: 85%;\"\n|-\n!Championship\n!colspan=\"2\" | Current champion(s)\n!Reign\n!Date won\n!Days<br />held\n!Location\n!Notes\n|-\n|align=center | [[NXT Championship]]\n|align=center | [[File:Adam Cole 2018.jpg|100px]]\n|align=center | [[Adam Cole]]\n|align=center | 1\n|align=center | June 1, 2019\n|align=center | {{age in days|month1=6|day1=1|year1=2019}} \n|align=center | [[Bridgeport, Connecticut]]\n|Defeated [[Johnny Gargano]] at [[NXT TakeOver: XXV|TakeOver: XXV]].\n|-\n|align=center | [[NXT Women's Championship]]\n|align=center | [[File:Charlotte Flair NOLA 2018.jpg|100px]]\n|align=center | [[Charlotte Flair]]\n|align=center | 2\n|align=center | March 25 or 26, 2020\n|align=center | {{age in days nts|March 25, 2020}} or {{age in days nts|March 26, 2020}}\n|align=center | [[Orlando, Florida]]\n|Defeated [[Rhea Ripley]] during [[WrestleMania 36]] Part 2.<br/>{{small|Aired on [[tape delay]] on April 5, 2020.}}\n|-\n|align=center | [[NXT North American Championship]]\n|align=center |[[File:Keith Lee April 2018.jpg|100px]]\n|align=center | [[Keith Lee (wrestler)|Keith Lee]]\n|align=center | 1\n|align=center | January 22, 2020\n|align=center | {{age in days|month1=1|day1=22|year1=2020}}\n|align=center | [[Winter Park, Florida]]\n|Defeated [[Roderick Strong]] on ''[[WWE NXT|NXT]]''.\n|-\n|align=center | [[NXT Tag Team Championship]]\n|align=center | [[File:The BroserWeights.jpg|100px]]\n|align=center | The BroserWeights<br>{{small|([[Matt Riddle]] and [[Pete Dunne]])}}\n|align=center | 1\n|align=center | February 16, 2020\n|align=center | {{age in days|